'''Petroglyph''' is a game studio based in [[Wikipedia:Las Vegas, Nevada|Las Vegas]], [[Wikipedia:Nevada|Nevada]]. The studio was founded [[April 1]], [[2003]] by former employees of [[Electronic Arts]]. Petroglyph is primarily known for their unusually strong experience in [[Wikipedia:Real-time strategy|RTS]] game development. The company's founding members have worked on seminal and influential games in the genre, most notably [[Wikipedia:Command and Conquer|''Command & Conquer'']] and recently ''[[Star Wars: Empire at War]]''.

